    "Specifically, we use six dis-tinct semantic categories defined in HarmBench as separate domains: Chemical Biological, Misinformation, Illegel, Cybercrime, Harmful, and Harassment Bully.",
    "The general GCG-M without domain data training serves as the baseline.",
    "We also include experiments using GCG-M trained with the same domain data.",
    "To ensure a fair comparison, all experiments maintain the same total search steps, 500.",
    "The experimental results for both validation and test sets are displayed in Fig. 3."
